line_1: Or why, as Years our Frame attack,
line_2: Our Hair grows white, our Teeth grow black?

line_1: Why paces three return to the attack?
line_2: Why must Impatience fall three paces back?

line_1: And guard the point no enemies attack.
line_2: Who simple truth with nine-fold reasons back,

line_1: If when the furious storms attack,
line_2: Direct, O Lord, the wanderers back

line_1: And when they next the hostile Wall attack,
line_2: Feel the Heart fail, the lifted Arm grow slack;

line_1: While MARLBRÔ presses to the dire Attack,
line_2: Seated on Rocks her proud Foundations shake,

line_1: All side in Parties, and begin th' Attack;
line_2: Fans clap, Silks russle, and tough Whalebones crack;
